public interface Reference extends Element
A representation of the model object 'Reference'. Reference is an element that references a member of an ontology, in order to add other annotations to it.

The following features are supported:

  • Owned Annotations

    • getOwnedAnnotations

      org.eclipse.emf.common.util.EList<Annotation> getOwnedAnnotations()
      Returns the value of the 'Owned Annotations' containment reference list. The list contents are of type Annotation. It is bidirectional and its opposite is 'Owning Reference'. A set of annotations added to the referenced member by this reference

      the value of the 'Owned Annotations' containment reference list.
